  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >By playing <strong>Smart Gecko</strong> you will stimulate your motor cognition, providing more mental agility in decision making. There are 60 challenging levels... Have fun playing Smart Gecko!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067100/extras/973d90e8f77c8bdf9df0e773bd9030a8.poster.avif?t=1733500974\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067100/extras/973d90e8f77c8bdf9df0e773bd9030a8.webm?t=1733500974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067100/extras/973d90e8f77c8bdf9df0e773bd9030a8.mp4?t=1733500974\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Sokoban-like levels!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067100/extras/97cb5567e739292771eb1447d78d3ab3.poster.avif?t=1733500974\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067100/extras/97cb5567e739292771eb1447d78d3ab3.webm?t=1733500974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067100/extras/97cb5567e739292771eb1447d78d3ab3.mp4?t=1733500974\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In addition to having fun playing, you can relieve your stress, improve your reflexes in a physical activity and make your daily tasks much more productive!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067100/extras/7b2e83a1a9eb44db6d2cfbfa39a63a77.poster.avif?t=1733500974\" width=600 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067100/extras/7b2e83a1a9eb44db6d2cfbfa39a63a77.webm?t=1733500974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067100/extras/7b2e83a1a9eb44db6d2cfbfa39a63a77.mp4?t=1733500974\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Action Puzzle!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >60 challenging levels!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>JigSaw Puzzle Mode!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067100/extras/398ce3638149d5e4e73392a50175cf29.poster.avif?t=1733500974\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067100/extras/398ce3638149d5e4e73392a50175cf29.webm?t=1733500974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067100/extras/398ce3638149d5e4e73392a50175cf29.mp4?t=1733500974\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Keyboard or <strong>Mouse gameplay</strong>!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067100/extras/d02af284bb50e3f7be1175b62f12bf77.poster.avif?t=1733500974\" width=600 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067100/extras/d02af284bb50e3f7be1175b62f12bf77.webm?t=1733500974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067100/extras/d02af284bb50e3f7be1175b62f12bf77.mp4?t=1733500974\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >and more: </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level Tips!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immersive Soundtrack!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067100/extras/2eb10a11bbf31f1d3a05e6ca88515ada.poster.avif?t=1733500974\" width=600 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067100/extras/2eb10a11bbf31f1d3a05e6ca88515ada.webm?t=1733500974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067100/extras/2eb10a11bbf31f1d3a05e6ca88515ada.mp4?t=1733500974\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >History:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a research laboratory, one scientist in particular develops an experiment with a gecko, being one of the most agile and clever reptiles in its food chain.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >He trains his 'Tixaz' gecko in rooms designed to develop his abilities, and as reward and motivation, he gives him to eat special flies that give more intelligence</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067100/extras/77e4104d26e8a1c3d8547e29ef284392.avif?t=1733500974\" width=600 height=180 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be the gecko, and show us how clever and fun your experience can be in the challenges that will be given to you.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >By playing <strong>Smart Gecko</strong> you will stimulate your motor cognition, providing more mental agility in decision making. There are 60 challenging levels... Have fun playing Smart Gecko!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067100/extras/973d90e8f77c8bdf9df0e773bd9030a8.poster.avif?t=1733500974\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067100/extras/973d90e8f77c8bdf9df0e773bd9030a8.webm?t=1733500974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067100/extras/973d90e8f77c8bdf9df0e773bd9030a8.mp4?t=1733500974\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Sokoban-like levels!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067100/extras/97cb5567e739292771eb1447d78d3ab3.poster.avif?t=1733500974\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067100/extras/97cb5567e739292771eb1447d78d3ab3.webm?t=1733500974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067100/extras/97cb5567e739292771eb1447d78d3ab3.mp4?t=1733500974\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In addition to having fun playing, you can relieve your stress, improve your reflexes in a physical activity and make your daily tasks much more productive!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067100/extras/7b2e83a1a9eb44db6d2cfbfa39a63a77.poster.avif?t=1733500974\" width=600 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067100/extras/7b2e83a1a9eb44db6d2cfbfa39a63a77.webm?t=1733500974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067100/extras/7b2e83a1a9eb44db6d2cfbfa39a63a77.mp4?t=1733500974\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Action Puzzle!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >60 challenging levels!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>JigSaw Puzzle Mode!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067100/extras/398ce3638149d5e4e73392a50175cf29.poster.avif?t=1733500974\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067100/extras/398ce3638149d5e4e73392a50175cf29.webm?t=1733500974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067100/extras/398ce3638149d5e4e73392a50175cf29.mp4?t=1733500974\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Keyboard or <strong>Mouse gameplay</strong>!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067100/extras/d02af284bb50e3f7be1175b62f12bf77.poster.avif?t=1733500974\" width=600 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1067100/extras/d02af284bb50e3f7be1175b62f12bf77.webm?t=1733500974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"